      "span_text": "They revealed that the reduced mechanism showed very close results to measured species profiles of C 2 H 4 compared to the detailed one, and with soot volume fractions obtained from Engine Combustion Network (ECN) spray H experiments. This reduced PAH mechanism was incorporated with the TPGME mechanism of this study to develop a reduced TPGME-n-hexadecane-PAH mechanism."
